<div id="review_1331329163" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1331329163" />
    <a title="Lorraine Lipman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/28393160-lorraine-lipman"><img alt="Lorraine Lipman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1465694668p2/28393160.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1331329163?book_show_action=true">Jul 10, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lorraine Lipman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lorraine Lipman" href="/user/show/28393160-lorraine-lipman">Lorraine Lipman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1331329163" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13328407011002373009">I really enjoyed this novel. The notion of reunions is always scary and the relationships rediscovered didn&apos;t disappoint. The subplot novel, written by Agnes was also interesting and parallels the main plot. It is a novel about unfolding relationships. So if you are looking for an action thriller this is not the book for you.</span>
  <span id="freeText13328407011002373009" style="display:none">I really enjoyed this novel. The notion of reunions is always scary and the relationships rediscovered didn't disappoint. The subplot novel, written by Agnes was also interesting and parallels the main plot. It is a novel about unfolding relationships. So if you are looking for an action thriller this is not the book for you.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13328407011002373009" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
