<div id="review_3012111636" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3012111636" />
    <a title="Julia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17321413-julia"><img alt="Julia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1559373470p2/17321413.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3012111636?book_show_action=true">Dec 27, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Julia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Julia" href="/user/show/17321413-julia">Julia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780349117997" href="/book/show/828711.A_Wedding_in_December">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3012111636" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10369096598101623316">With quite a few characters to get my head around, it took me a while to get into it but once I did, I found it readable. Maybe not as good as some of her other books, imo. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


