s are afflicted with many of the same ailments as humans their treatment often raises special problems. He has learned how to anaesthetize a giraffe without letting the animal injure its fragile neck in a fall, how to enlist the cooperation of a frightened pachyderm who must undergo an operation, and how to administer an enema to an enraged Siberian tiger. He recounts the hilarious story of the night he transported a whale overland with the aid of several thousand popsicles when no ice was to be found, and the difficulties of performing the first Caesarean ever done on a zebra while coping with his own allergy to the animal.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"16010166308599452285\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'21_book_2131858\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"kF7XsquhIiIjhw7fYl8nZhJvgASHAgX4x0CqRBnnDebyKTJVn0PqBimGfRnKUqzBPRYFWgJFsL/xkkbfxjOB0A==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"2131858\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"21_book_2131858\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"pa